list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Added a game Selection wich dynamicly displays games, it also has animations, furthermore i did some minor bug fixes and added a back button to the login screen.

task.summary: Completely redone Class Design using a major State Machine to handle the different Scenes which are now loaded by the Model. Also i've implemented an abstract class for the Model so there's no duplicate and other Obsolete code in the model. also i'm using a Controller interface and a custom Observer for more convenient use.
Fit all classes to the newly implemented Design and added the functionality to open two windows at once.
implemented some extra logic for the sign in process and updated some fxml sheets
